### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts

### Get single contact by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/69aa5f569ef8d3311f0852b1

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-06-15"
}

### Update a contact by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/69aa5f569ef8d3311f0852b1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1990-06-15"
}

### Delete a contact by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/69aa5f569ef8d3311f0852b1

